title: Logo for Newsletter about Recreational Sports Business
description:
This logo is for a new Substack newsletter around the Recreational Sports Industry.
Straight from Alan Arlt, the founder of Ultimate Hoops, Inc. comes inspiration, education, and motivation to launch your own Recreational Sports Business.
From the About Page:
Why subscribe?
The Rec Sports Life is a weekly newsletter about the Recreational Sports Industry. The purpose of the newsletter is to inspire you to start your own recreational sports business and give you the guidance and tools to succeed.
I’ll share my experience and behind-the-scenes from my 15 years of starting and operating my own recreational sports business, Ultimate Hoops Inc., acquired by Life Time, Inc. and grew into the premier nationwide network of recreational basketball leagues in the U.S.
This newsletter is intended to create meaningful conversations around the Recreational Sports Industry and band together to create more rec sports experiences for people to live happy, healthy lives through sports and community.
What reading The Rec Sports Life will benefit you:
The Rec Sports Life is aimed at current or aspiring recreational sports business owners. Today, it’s never been a better time for the recreational sports market. Post-pandemic, participation is back on course, driven by the millennial generation’s love of recreational sports combined with the limitless digital platforms to build a thriving community engaged in your business 24/7. 
Whether you’re a startup or an established player in the recreational sports market, the proven approach and methodologies presented in this newsletter will take your business to new levels of profitability, operational performance, and brand loyalty.
And your customers will love you for it. 
Let’s get started.
other_color_requirements:
I prefer a logogram style that represents the sports world /culture. This request doesn't mean it must be a baseball, soccer ball, or basketball. This logo should inspire others to learn more about the recreational sports industry and business without feeling too corporate.
(I know, a tough challenge!) :)
other_notes: Please make sure the logo reflects sophistication and luxury. The logo should NOT look like a “beer league” recreational sports logo. This is for a weekly business publication, promoting consulting services and delivering business insights. Thanks!

Our manufacturing process undergoes continuous quality control, inspected by our own teams, in addition to third parties with independent certification.
As a product nears it's final phase, it is tested by world-classing testing facilities to ensure the product meets maximum performance.
Our products are manufactured in a FDA registered Facility, and made in the USA.
